The trolls are certainly one reason that some people have left.

Also, our audience has fractured.  Message boards like Silentcomedians.com
( http://www.silentcomedians.com/forum/index.php ), Louise Brooks
( http://lbs.proboards24.com/index.cgi?board=general ), Harold Lloyd
( http://pub39.ezboard.com/ftheharoldlloydcommunityfrm1 ), Golden Silents
( http://goldensilents.proboards46.com/index.cgi?board=general ) and the Yahoo
silent groups ( http://movies.groups.yahoo.com/group/silentfilms/messages is
one) have attracted people who didn't have time to read all of the a.m.s.
postings, or who were tired of listening to the trolls on alt.movies.silent.

Finally, it is summertime.  So people are not in front of their computers as
much.

Still, I'm surprised that nobody has posted any reviews of the San Francisco
Silent Film Festival yet.

--
